When he was dying,
he was always cheerful, he was lovely.

513
00:37:58,020 --> 00:38:00,466
Except when he thought no one could see.

514
00:38:01,500 --> 00:38:05,186
- I saw him once. He looked sad.
- Molly...

515
00:38:06,260 --> 00:38:09,469
