for the execution.

586
00:42:37,060 --> 00:42:40,223
Murder by remote control.
He could be 1,000 miles away.

587
00:42:44,100 --> 00:42:46,068
The hungrier they got,
the more they ate,

588
00:42:46,460 --> 00:42:48,383
