589
00:42:48,540 --> 00:42:49,780
Sherlock.

590
00:42:49,860 --> 00:42:51,749
Over here!

591
00:42:53,540 --> 00:42:55,463
We've got you, don't worry.

592
00:43:03,260 --> 00:43:05,547
Right, then.
The professionals have finished

593
