00:45:18,380 --> 00:45:21,270
- sent from us here at London...
- Could you turn that off, please?

627
00:45:21,340 --> 00:45:23,911
As you can see,
the set comprises of a beautiful...

628
00:45:23,980 --> 00:45:25,345
Can you turn this off?

